{"tid":1951321,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人股票投資 101 【二世祖有家底廢柴亦係你老闆】","createTime":"2020-03-31T02:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:04:50.000Z","uid":125976,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"69f56a45cfe711e44f4819b29dfbceee105c7036","tid":1951321,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:08:36.000Z","msg":"開始講𠵱個行業之前，送大家兩句金句：<br />\n有錢，廢柴可以做老闆<br />\n冇錢，天才都要做撚狗<br />\n<br />\n𠵱個喺八字上係一個位階嘅概念，就係咁撚唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係話，相同嘅八字，如果出生喺唔同地區、家庭，佢嘅人生都會唔同,好正路呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁講，假設你同我今年都係行梗破財運，但你係有家底而我冇，你可能只係𠵱段時間身痕買咗好多名牌同屌咗好多女，而我如果而家做梗生意就即係收皮之日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，你話點解扯咁遠講八字又講二世祖，我都唔撚信嘅，其實同今日所講嘅行業好有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n我所講嘅行業就係壽險股，但我而家開始唔會講好長，因為你哋有基本認識想深入研究自然會自己研究，講真嗰句我揼 code 點都叻過炒股，只不過喺廢港冇運行啫，好啦唔講𠵱啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壽險股點解似二世祖？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋鬥梗兩樣嘢：<br />\n1. 家底（EV 保單內含價值）<br />\n2. cap 新水能力（NBV 一年保單新業務價值）<br />\n<br />\n佢哋又可以分成兩類<br />\nA. 家底厚而鳩吹 cap 水能力強<br />\nB. 家底厚但鳩吹 cap 水能力麻麻<br />\n<br />\n面對 A 類 eg. 1299, 2318，我哋會用以下公式<br />\n<br />\n<code>市值 = 一倍EV + NBV &times; Multiple</code><br />\n<br />\n即係就算佢低位點都計一倍家底嘅價值落去，但佢嘅 cap 水能力我哋會好似乘返相應倍數嘅 P/E 咁<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟個 multiple 低同高位大概幾多，每隻都唔同，自己搵幾年股價高低位做統計啦（其實我個 殘.ga 已經有）<br />\n<br />\n而對於 B 類(eg. 1336, 2601 etc.) 賺錢唔夠叻嘅二世祖，我哋會用 P/EV，即係佢嘅將家底打折囉。都係啦，高低位自己統計。<br />\n<br />\n另外你可能會問到點解有啲 Multiple 個底低啲，有啲高啲，咁你考慮埋佢哋「三差」：<br />\n1. 利差（Interest Margin)<br />\n2. 費差（Expense Margin）<br />\n3. 死差（Mortality Margin）<br />\n<br />\n自己 Google 啦，唔解啦，夠鐘幫條二世祖揼垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"http://bennychungwai.blogspot.com/2017/04/sotp.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbennychungwai.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F04%2Fsotp.html%3Fm%3D1&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=be2ca2c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bennychungwai.blogspot.com/2017/04/sotp.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"9ef55529908325a6375e189c4fb1cf44f42da3c6","tid":1951321,"uid":254388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69b24178b0d1f92e2885dc9cbe327a49eb291e8f","tid":1951321,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"講真嗰句，而家得 B 類先多水位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325c081c0744126374717d5cc4e008ddb62aaabf","tid":1951321,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打有心<br />\n祝你唔洗做撚狗"},{"pid":"4814c874861122a77c5c74b6f81cfadc95df6c0b","tid":1951321,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"1299 今年返唔返到80蚊"},{"pid":"dc64e3e01027ec09e7fcb16523d22d0a101e113e","tid":1951321,"uid":313363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"但大陸股信唔信得過<br />\n支那經濟就爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206bda52ea4825e6cb30397062e8997805af210d","tid":1951321,"uid":313363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4814c874861122a77c5c74b6f81cfadc95df6c0b","tid":1951321,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"1299 今年返唔返到80蚊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"師兄咩價位入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dee4aaa6798b63257312083d70086f57281c427","tid":1951321,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"206bda52ea4825e6cb30397062e899